; ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
; Unit Test Preamble
; ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
;
; Built-in assertions and utilities for the unit test harness.
; This preamble is automatically included in every test.

; (assert! cond code) — abort with code if cond is false
(defmacro assert! (cond code)
  (when (not cond) (abort! code)))
